; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/common/openclaw-message.md

% openclaw-message, common

# Send a message to a phone number (WhatsApp)
openclaw message send <__t___target_> <_1234567890> <__m___message_> "<Hello>"

# Send a message to a specific channel
openclaw message send --channel <telegram> <__t___target_> <user_id> <__m___message_> "<Hello>"

# Display help
openclaw message <__h___help_>
